Description: Shiny applications to compare and explore the IPBES biodiversity
    glossary and the IPCC climate change glossary. The comparison app aligns
    terms, computes similarity scores, shows word-level differences, and
    visualizes a directed term hierarchy. The glossary explorer app provides
    source-specific term lookup with linked in-definition navigation. Hosted-safe
    deployment modes are included for shinyapps.io.
